title: I Love Pokémon With Guns...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at Palworld. This game really dropped out of nowhere and happens to be the best monster catching experience that gives Game Freak and The Pokemon Company a complete run for their money. Thanks for watching!
